(906, 108, 'neurological_consultation_paragraph', 'Dandenong Neurology is a full service clinic specialising in neurology, neuropsychology and geriatric services. Our professional\r\n team of highly skilled neurologists, specialists and therapists, diagnose and treat all types of neurological and psychological \r\ndisorders with a focus on providing our patients with a higher quality of life.'),
