(1421, 160, 'description_upper_meet_team', 'At Dandenong Neurology, we provide a complete range of neurological, neuropsychological, geriatric and allied health\r\nservices in a friendly and comfortable environment. Our highly-skilled medical team includes Greater Dandenong’s finest \r\nneurologists, specialists and medical professionals are committed to helping our patients enjoy a higher quality of life.'),
