(4944, 333, 'patient_information_form_paragraph', 'Please use the contact form below for general enquiries regarding our practice and we will respond as quickly as possible. Our \r\npriority is your happiness, health, and longevity, and we believe the best way to achieve this is through a thoughtful combination \r\nof traditional and alternative medicine.'),
